enum bitMapType
 

The different types of bitmaps that need to be supported.

The server will not send a bitmap of the wrong type to a client which does not support it.

Enumeration values:
png 
gif 
wbmp

enum capStyle
 

The style of the line endings.

Enumeration values:
flatCap  The lines end and their end coordinate.
squareCap  The lines are extended by half their width.
roundCap  The lines are ended by a circle with the width as diameter.

enum dashStyle
 

The different dash styles of the pen.

Enumeration values:
nullDash  The pen will not draw.
solidDash  The pen is solid.
dottedDash  A dotted line.
dashedDash  A dashed line - - - -.
